'''飓风莱斯特'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Lester}}）是[[1998年太平洋飓风季|1998年太平洋飓风季]]形成的第15个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，第12场获命名的风暴和第八场飓风。系统源自9月29日离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]的[[东风波|东风波]]，由于外界环境不利，直至10月15日才成为热带低气压。气旋当天就升级成热带风暴，次日又达到飓风标准。经过一段时间的强度波动，莱斯特达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]185公里的最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]已属三级飓风标准。风暴此后逐渐减弱，于10月26日降级成热带风暴，并在不久后完全消散。

气旋自始至终没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但10月18日行进至距陆地最近的位置时产生暴雨和中等强度风力。降水引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，夺走两名孩童的生命，风暴整体引起的损失数额缺乏统计。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Lester 1998 track.png}}
1998年9月29日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]。10月5日，东风波沿线的一片[[对流|对流]]区发展成[[1998年大西洋飓风季#飓风丽莎|大西洋飓风丽莎]]。东风波轴线部分继续向西前进，并在经过[[中美洲|中美洲]]后于10月13日在[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]和[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]边境以南约275公里洋面发展出下层环流。系统向西北方向飘移，中心周围的对流逐渐增长，开始形成[[雨带|带状特征]]。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月15日凌晨0点，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将系统归类成[[1998年太平洋飓风季|1998年太平洋飓风季]]第十四{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。<ref name="lestertcr">{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | year = 1998 | title = Hurricane Lester Preliminary Report | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP141998_Lester.pdf | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002015216/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP141998_Lester.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>气旋内有大范围对流活动，所在洋面又存在[[海面温度|水温]]偏高、[[风切变|垂直风切变]]少、外流良好等多重利好条件，所以得以逐渐增强<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E Discussion Number 1 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231608/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.001 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.001 | date =  }}</ref>。气象机构起初难以确定系统的准确动向，只是预计气旋会向西北方向移动<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E Discussion Number 2 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202936/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.002 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.002 | date =  }}</ref>。10月15日早上，卫星图像表明环流中心的位置在此前预测位置的东北方向<ref>{{Cite report | author = Edward Rappaport | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E Discussion Number 3 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211144/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.003 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.003 | date =  }}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}下午14点，[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动经过组织已朝中心靠拢<ref>{{Cite report | author = Edward Rappaport | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E Discussion Number 4 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233621/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.004 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.004 | date =  }}</ref>，热带低气压到{{lang|en|UTC}}18点时已升级成热带风暴并获名“莱斯特”（{{lang|en|Lester}}）<ref name="lestertcr" />。

不久后，风暴略朝西面转向<ref>{{Cite report | author = John Guiney | title = Tropical Storm Lester Discussion Number 5 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165250/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.005 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.005 | date =  }}</ref>，与此同时外流开始局限在西南象限的环流内<ref>{{Cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Tropical Storm Lester Discussion Number 6 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.006 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210859/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.006 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}10月16日下午14点，[[侦察机|侦察机]]所测数据证明气旋已达飓风标准，最低中心[[气压|气压]]降至992[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）<ref>{{Cite report | author = Edward Rappaport | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 8 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.008 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.008 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。10月17日清晨，环形的深层对流内首度呈现出存在[[风眼|风眼]]的迹象，莱斯特此时正以每小时9.7公里左右的速度朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动<ref>{{Cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 10 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021031857/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.010 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.010 | date =  }}</ref>。不久后，飓风因北侧有短波槽经过而一度几乎停止移动<ref name="lestertcr" />，然后很快就达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准<ref>{{Cite report | author = Edward Rappaport | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 11 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224135/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.011 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.011 | date =  }}</ref>。10月18日清晨，莱斯特的风眼有小幅弱化，顶端云层组成的环状云系略显混乱，令气旋连续数小时无法进一步增强<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 14 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.014 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.014 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午14点，系统风速提升到每小时160公里，并行进至墨西哥瓦哈卡州以南约110公里洋面，这也是风暴存在期间距陆地最近的一刻<ref name="lestertcr" />。当晚，莱斯特减弱成一级飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 18 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.018 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175121/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.018 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>，但很快就开始再度强化<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 19 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021041152/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.019 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.019 | date =  }}</ref>。

10月19日，风暴环流开始受到中至上层低气压系统产生的垂直风切变影响，因此略有弱化<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | title = Hurricane Lester Discussion Number 20 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215701/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.020 | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.020 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但到了10月20日清晨，飓风又经过重新组织而再度增强<ref name="lestertcr" />。10月22日，莱斯特在[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]西南方向约570公里海域达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]185公里的最高强度，同时还因[[低压槽|短波槽]]影响几乎停止前进，然后再转向西南并逐渐弱化<ref name="lestertcr" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月23日凌晨2点，飓风因深层对流迅速消退而弱化成一级飓风<ref name="lestertcr" />，再于当天上午在朝西南方向移动期间降级成热带风暴<ref>{{Cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Tropical Storm Lester Discussion Number 35 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.035 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230330/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.035 | date =  }}</ref>。到了10月24日，下层环流中心已从云系中暴露出来<ref>{{Cite report | author = Brian Jarvinen | title = Tropical Storm Lester Discussion Number 41 | year = 1998 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.041 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NEP1498.041 | date =  }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月16日凌晨0点，莱斯特在[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端西南方向约805公里洋面消退成热带低气压，并在不久后逐渐消散<ref name="lestertcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Lester1998filledrainwhite.gif|right]]
面对风暴威胁，墨西哥政府向[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]][[阿里斯塔港|阿里斯塔港]]（{{lang|en|Puerto Arista}}）到蓬塔马尔多纳多（{{lang|en|Punta Maldonaldo}}）之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，之后又向瓦哈卡州[[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）到[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]地区发布飓风警告。危地马拉[[埃斯昆特拉省|埃斯昆特拉省]]度假小镇[[锡帕卡特|锡帕卡特]]（{{lang|en|Sipacate}}）到墨西哥阿里斯塔港间区域收到热带风暴警告。<ref name="lestertcr" />墨西哥有关部门下令将南海岸沿线约3000居民转移到500个应急避难所<ref name="bg1018">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 1998-10-18 | title = Thousands flee Mexico coast as Hurricane Lester nears}}</ref>。

风暴令危地马拉西南部普降暴雨，该国太平洋海岸局部地区测得高达228毫米雨量。飓风令[[西马德雷山脉|西马德雷山脉]]东北边缘的空气湿度大幅上升，致使上山坡一侧的狭窄地带出现强降雨，局部最高雨量达360毫米。<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2007 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/lester1998.html | title = Hurricane Lester - October 13-22, 1998 | accessdate = 2016-05-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080509/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/lester1998.html | date =  }}</ref>据报导，墨西哥南部沿海地区测得热带风暴强度大风<ref name="lestertcr" />。降水导致部分房屋被毁，多头牲畜死亡，还引发夺走两名孩童性命的[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref name="ch1017">{{cite news | newspaper = Calgary Herald | date = 1998-10-17 | title = Weather Kills Two in Guatemala}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Hurricane kills two, heads for Mexican coast leaves flooding in Guatemala | year = 1998 | newspaper = ''San Jose Mercury News''}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | agency = Accosiated Press | title = Storm kills two in Guatemala, roars toward southern Mexico | year = 1998 | newspaper = ''Fort Worth Star-Telegram''}}</ref>。气旋产生的降水导致[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]一座桥梁被毁，约1000人的交通出行受到影响<ref name="xinhua1017">{{cite news | agency = [[新华社|Xinhua News Agency]] | date = 1998-10-17 | title = Heavy Rains Bring Bridge Down in Honduras}}</ref>。恰帕斯州也降下暴雨，引起河流泛滥，但具体破坏程度缺乏报导<ref name="bg1018" />。

